! =================================================================
! ==== shared solver settings (included by every 5-BC-* deck) =====
! =================================================================
! Called via /INPUT at the start of each BC deck's solution phase.
! Single source for the nonlinear solver options and the results-output
! policy -- a tuning change here lands in every load stage at once
! instead of being copy-pasted nine times.

!! Solution
/solu
nropt,unsymmetric   ! unsymmetric Newton-Raphson (frictional contact)
neqit,50            ! max equilibrium iterations per substep
nlgeom,on           ! large-deflection effects
AUTOTS, ON          ! automatic substepping
DELTIM,0.05,,,ON
CUTCONTROL,PLSLIMIT,1

! Results-output policy. The postprocess decks (7-PP, 8-PP-*) read nodal
! displacements + reaction forces at EVERY substep (fd curves) but element
! data only at the current set when they run (area_summary via ETABLE,VOLU).
! Writing the full element solution at every substep (the old outres,all,all)
! inflates the .rst by roughly an order of magnitude for data nothing reads.
! Set full_output = 1 below to restore write-everything (debug / field plots).
full_output = 0
*IF,full_output,EQ,1,THEN
    outres,all,all
*ELSE
    outres,all,none
    outres,nsol,all     ! nodal DOF solution, every substep
    outres,rsol,all     ! reaction loads, every substep
    outres,esol,last    ! element solution, last substep of each load step
*ENDIF
